cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata below."
type: software
title: "UniversalNumbers.jl: Next-generation computer arithmetic in Julia"
abstract: >-
  Julia bindings to the Stillwater Universal C++ library, exposing posits,
  classic floats (cfloat), logarithmic number systems, takums, fixed-point,
  IBM hexadecimal floats, decimal floats, bfloat16, and double-double as
  first-class AbstractFloat types under one consistent interface.
authors:
